official_title: A bill to continue mandatory price support for tung nuts only through the 1976 crop.

summary.text: Provides that the mandatory price support for tung nuts through the 1976 crop shall be supported at a level not in excess of 90% nor less than 60% of the parity price (existing law omits time limitation). (Amends 7 U.S.C. 1446 (b))

titles.title: A bill to continue mandatory price support for tung nuts only through the 1976 crop.
